  "detailed_description": "Are you ready for some 70s’ disco fever with Dave and the rest of the gang? Disco Dave is a quick fun game with voxel graphics. Test your reflexes in the neon disco environment, stay alive and perform combos to get extra points. Watch the floor tiles change colour, and stay away from the gray ones! Use your coins to unlock new characters with far out style and animations.",
